Position and patency were confirmed.

Indication: {{ indication }}.

The patient tolerated the exchange without complications.
{% endmacro %}


{# --- Stoma or Tracheal Granulation — Mechanical Debridement --- #}
{% macro granulation_debridement(site, debridement_tool, hemostasis_method, trach_exchanged=false) %}
